<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="es"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/><title>CI2T :: Congreso Internacional de Tecnologia Tijuana ::: home</title><style>@font-face{font-family:BebasNeue;font-weight:normal;src:url("/public/font/BebasNeue-Regular.ttf")}@font-face{font-family:BebasNeue;font-weight:bold;src:url("/public/font/BebasNeue-Bold.otf")}@font-face{font-family:Roboto;font-weight:normal;src:url("/public/font/Roboto-Regular.ttf")}@font-face{font-family:Roboto;font-weight:bold;src:url("/public/font/Roboto-Bold.ttf")}*{margin:0;padding:0;border:0}:root{--color-dark:#000;--color-dark-2:#060606;--color-light:#fff;--color-light-2:#838383;--color-orange:#ff9700;--color-bg-primary:var(--color-dark);--color-bg-secundary:var(--color-dark-2);--color-text-primary:var(--color-light);--color-text-secundary:var(--color-light-2);--color-accent:var(--color-orange)}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}body{font-family:BebasNeue;background-color:var(--color-bg-primary);color:var(--color-text-primary);background-image:url("public/images/background.png");background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position:center center;background-size:cover;background-attachment:fixed}body::-webkit-scrollbar{width:8px;height:100vh}a{text-decoration:none}.container{width:80%;padding:0 10%;padding-bottom:4em}.white{background-color:var(--color-light);color:var(--color-dark);padding-top:8em}.link{font-size:1.2em;text-decoration:none;color:var(--color-text-primary)}#info{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;font-size:3em;line-height:1.25em;margin:0 1em;height:calc(100vh - 5em);padding-bottom:5em}.data{grid-column:2/3;margin:auto 0}.data h3{font-size:.75em}.accent{color:var(--color-accent)}.highlight{border-radius:.3em;padding:0 .5em;background-color:var(--color-accent)}.btn-option{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:.5em}.btn-option *{width:49%}.btn{outline:none;font-family:BebasNeue;font-weight:bold;font-size:.4em;background-color:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;padding:1em 1.5em;text-space:4px;cursor:pointer}.btn-primary{background-color:#fff;border:2px solid #fff;color:#000}.btn-secondary{border:2px solid #fff;color:#fff}.container h1{font-size:4em}p{font-family:Roboto;font-size:2em;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:2em}:root{--navbar-height:8em}nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:var(--navbar-height);padding:0 calc(var(--navbar-height) / 2)}nav #logo{font-size:4em;margin-right:.5em}nav #logo::after{content:"";position:relative;background-color:var(--color-text-primary);width:1px;height:.75em;margin-left:.5em}nav *{display:flex;align-items:center}nav .lang{margin:0 .2em}nav .active{color:var(--color-text-secundary)}.burger{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;height:2em;margin-left:1.5em;cursor:pointer}.line{user-select:none;width:4em;height:4px;background-color:var(--color-text-primary)}.line:nth-child(2){width:3em}.conferences{padding-bottom:4em}.conferences h1{padding-bottom:1em}.conference{padding:1em;font-family:Roboto;margin:2em 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:3em 1fr;grid-gap:1em;align-items:center;transition:200ms}.conference:hover{transition:200ms;transform:translate(-1em,-1em);box-shadow:.5em .5em 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}.conference a,.conference .description{grid-column:2/3}.conference a{font-family:Roboto;margin:1em 0;font-weight:bold;color:var(--color-accent)}.conference .description{font-size:1.5em;text-align:justify}.conference *{margin:0;padding:0}.conference i{height:3em;background:var(--color-accent);font-style:normal;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;font-family:BebasNeue;font-weight:bold;text-space:4px}.simposio{font-weight:bold}#poster{color:var(--color-accent) !important;display:flex;justify-content:center}#footer{background:var(--color-bg-primary);padding:2em 10%}</style></head><body><nav><div class="start"><h1 id="logo">CI2T</h1><a class="link" href="/public/images/CI2T-2020_general-program.png" target="_blank"><h2>Programa</h2></a></div><div class="center"></div><div class="end"><div class="idioma"><a class="link lang" href="/en"><h2>EN</h2></a><a class="link lang active" href="/"><h2>ES</h2></a></div><div class="burger"><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div></div></div></nav><div id="info"><div class="data"><h2>congreso internacional <br>de tecnologia tijuana</h2><h3 class="accent">baja california, mexico | 24 - 26 oct</h3><div class="btn-option"><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#">Cede del evento</a><a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Conferencia virtual</a></div></div></div><section class="container" id="about"><h1>La <span class="accent">cede del ci2t</span> <br>sera en las instalaciones <br>de la <span class="highlight">uabc</span></h1><p>Organizado por la Facultad de Ciencias Químicas e Ingeniería, como una plataforma de diseminación bilingüe para profesores, investigadores, estudiantes, graduados, y profesionistas, donde trabajos teoricos y/o prácticos serán presentados, además de promover nexos entre expertos y la industria.</p><a class="link" href="http://www.uabc.mx/" target="_blank"><p class="accent">Visitar sitio de la universidad →</p></a></section><section class="white container" id="conferences"><h1>El evento <span class="accent">se compone</span><br> de las siguientes pistas</h1><div class="conferences"><div class="conference" id="cocsce"><i>3er</i><p class="simposio">Jornada de Informática e Informática e Ingeniería</p><p class="description">All submitted papers with be held under peer review before acceptance to the conference. Accepted papers will be either chosen for oral presentation or for poster presentation, depending on the quality and contribution of submitted work...</p><a href="/cocsce">Leer mas →</a></div><div class="conference" id="coee"><i>3er</i><p class="simposio">Conferencia sobre Ingeniería Electrónica</p><p class="description">All submitted papers with be held under peer review before acceptance to the conference. Accepted papers will be either chosen for oral presentation or for poster presentation, depending on the quality and contribution of submitted work...</p><a href="/coee">Leer mas →</a></div><div class="conference" id="icip"><i>3er</i><p class="simposio">Congreso Internacional de Proyectos Industriales</p><p class="description">All submitted papers with be held under peer review before acceptance to the conference. Accepted papers will be either chosen for oral presentation or for poster presentation, depending on the quality and contribution of submitted work...</p><a href="/icip">Leer mas →</a></div><div class="conference" id="mst"><i>3er</i><p class="simposio">Conferencia sobre Ciencias Químicas y Tecnología</p><p class="description">All submitted papers with be held under peer review before acceptance to the conference. Accepted papers will be either chosen for oral presentation or for poster presentation, depending on the quality and contribution of submitted work...</p><a href="/mst">Leer mas →</a></div><div class="conference" id="sasssi"><i>1er</i><p class="simposio">Simposio sobre ciencias aplicadas para resolver los problemas de la sociedad</p><p class="description">All submitted papers with be held under peer review before acceptance to the conference. Accepted papers will be either chosen for oral presentation or for poster presentation, depending on the quality and contribution of submitted work...</p><a href="/sasssi">Leer mas →</a></div></div><h1 id="poster"><a href="public/images/CI2T_2020_CFP.png" target="_blank">Download poster</a></h1></section><footer id="footer"><div id="copyright"><p>Copyright © 2020 por ci2tijuana.org | Todos los derechos reservados.</p></div></footer><script></script></body></html>